le\"; Romanian who poisoned two husbands in [[Nancy, France|Nancy]], and allegedly her first husband in her home country\n| <ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.estrepublicain.fr/actualite/2015/01/25/ils-m-ont-vole-ma-vie |title=Rodica Negroiu : \" Ils m'ont vol\u00e9 ma vie\u2026 \" |trans-title=Rodica Negroiu: \"They stole my life ...\" |first=\u00c9ric |last=Nicolas |date=25 January 2015 |newspaper=[[L'Est R\u00e9publicain]] |language=fr |access-date=28 January 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Yoni Palmier|Palmier, Yoni]]\n| 2011\u20132012\n| 4\n| 4\n| Sentenced to life imprisonment\n| Perpetrator of the [[Serial murders in Essonne|Essonne serial murders]]\n| <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://la1ere.francetvinfo.fr/2015/04/02/tueur-de-l-essonne-en-larmes-l-ex-petite-amie-raconte-sa-vie-avec-l-accuse-yoni-palmier-244471.html |title=Tueur de l'Essonne : en larmes, l'ex-petite amie raconte sa vie avec l'accus\u00e9, Yoni Palmier |trans-title=Killer of Essonne: in tears, the ex-girlfriend tells her life with the accused, Yoni Palmier |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=2 April 2015 |website=Outre-mer la 1\u00e8re |language=fr |access-date=24 November 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Thierry Paulin|Paulin, Thierry]]\n| 1984\u20131987\n| 18\n| 21\n| Died in prison\n| Known as \"The Beast of Montmarte\"; gay man who sexually assaulted and murdered old women in Paris\n| <ref>{{cite news |url=http://moreas.blog.lemonde.fr/2009/01/27/le-complice-du-tueur-des-vieilles-dames-est-libere-mathurin-paulin/ |title=Le complice du tueur des vieilles dames est lib\u00e9r\u00e9 |trans-title=The accomplice of the killer of the old ladies is released |last=Mor\u00e9as |first=G. |date=27 January 2009 |newspaper=[[Le Monde]] |language=fr |access-date=24 November 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Michel Peiry|Peiry, Michel]]\n| 1981\u20131987\n| 5\n| 11\n| Sentenced to life imprisonment\n| Known as \"The Sadist of Romont\"; Swiss soldier who sexually abused and murdered hitchhikers across several European countries 