ouardel |first=Paul |title=The Pel Affair |publisher=Bailli\u00e8re |date=1886 |page=48}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Marcel Petiot|Petiot, Marcel]]\n| 1926\u20131944\n| 27\n| 63+\n| Executed 1946\n| Doctor who murdered would-be refugees fleeing from the [[Nazi]]s\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.trutv.com/library/crime/serial_killers/history/petiot/5.html |title=Crime Library: Serial Killers: Dr. Marcel Petiot |first=Michael |last=Newton |website=TruTV.com |access-date=2013-06-11 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007230412/http://www.trutv.com/library/crime/serial_killers/history/petiot/5.html |archive-date=2012-10-07}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Louis Poirson|Poirson, Louis]]\n| 1995\u20132000\n| 4\n| 4\n| Sentenced to life imprisonment\n| Known as \"Rambo\"; [[Madagascar|Malagasy]]-born stonemason who kidnapped and raped women, killing four of them\n| <ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.leparisien.fr/faits-divers/plongee-dans-le-terrible-passe-du-tueur-en-serie-30-05-2002-2003110943.php |title=Plong\u00e9e dans le terrible pass\u00e9 du tueur en s\u00e9rie |trans-title=Diving into the terrible past of the serial killer |last=Albouy |first=St\u00e9phane |date=30 May 2002 |newspaper=[[Le Parisien]] |language=fr |access-date=24 November 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Victor Pr\u00e9vost|Pr\u00e9vost, Victor]]\n| 1877\u20131879\n| 2\n| 4\n| Executed 1880\n| Known as \"The Butcher of La Chapelle\"; former peacekeeper who murdered an acquaintance and his mistress; suspect in two disappearances\n| <ref>{{harvsp|La Lanterne|10/12/1880|p=1|id=LL}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Gilles de Rais|de Rais, Gilles]]\n| 15th-century\n| 400\n| 400+\n| Executed 1440\n| Compatriot of [[Joan of Arc]] and satanist who confessed to murdering scores of children\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.trutv.com/library/crime/serial_killers/predators/rais/execution_13.html |title=Gilles de Rais: The Pious Monster |first=Mark |last=Gribben |website=The Crime Library |accessdate=17 November 2011 |url-status=dead |ar